file.name: openapi_with_json_string_example.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: test
  description: foo
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: /
paths:
  /test:
    get:
      summary: foo
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
                format: uuid
                example: 06be83b3-5fb5-4103-a9b3-3fcd097a0634
